export default function timersDefault(id) {
    const timers = {
        updating: [0, 0, 30],
        strategy: [0, 1, 20],
        actions: [0, 1, 10],
        events: [0, 0, 15],
        debriefing: [0, 1, 15],
        satisfaction: [0, 0, 15],
        results: [0, 0, 15]
    }

    return ((id === 1) ? timers.updating :
        (id === 2) ? timers.strategy:
        (id === 3) ? timers.actions:
        (id === 4) ? timers.events:
        (id === 5) ? timers.debriefing:
        (id === 6) ? timers.satisfaction:
        (id === 7) ? timers.results: null)
}
